clamprotect (1.0.0-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * MCP Analytics Engine (stats, trends, recommendations, report tools).
  * MCP Reports Dashboard (live status, threat rate, recommendations).
  * Security Audit Dashboard (8 system-hardening checks).
  * VirusTotal hash lookup integrated into scan results.
  * On-access scanning (clamonacc) and USB auto-scan.
  * Scan profiles with JSON import/export.
  * Scan cancel support (both clamd and clamscan).
  * Quick Scan (5 common locations).
  * History CSV export.
  * Comprehensive README updated in EN/FR/AR.
  * PyQt6 enum compatibility fix.

 -- ClamProtect Team <team@clamprotect.local>  Fri, 26 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

